{"tid":965734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"甫宣誓就職 墨西哥一市長90分鐘後遭槍殺","createTime":"2019-01-02T09:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T10:09:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4d51ef79ce17d2ad68bd2c1e4099fe3fbf0b80c3","tid":965734,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:41:14.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕墨西哥一名市長才剛宣誓就職，就在前往市政廳途中遭槍擊，新市長僅就任幾小時就中彈身亡。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，墨西哥南部瓦哈卡州的特拉希亞科（Tlaxiaco）日前驚傳一起槍擊案，特拉希亞科市長聖地亞哥（Alejandro Aparicio Santiago）才剛剛宣誓就職，隨後在前往市政廳出席會議途中，遭數名槍手伏擊，市長中彈送醫不治，距離其宣誓就職僅90分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n除了市長外，還有4名同行受傷，其中一人傷勢嚴重，瓦哈卡州州長痛批這次槍擊案，稱已逮捕兇嫌，誓言會展開全面調查。<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥槍擊氾濫，政治人物受害尤為嚴重，據統計從2017年9月到2018年8月間，在短短1年之中就有850名政治人物遭槍擊，其中有175人不幸身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2659352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2659352&d=WzviOvFWrGNRmPFYDsyrJdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f22db4ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2659352&h=c0913509\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2659352</a>"},{"pid":"14b35bee609f1a2d03bf281fde9706c6b3c81154","tid":965734,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"又要換市長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1496196393b746f596f3033364ace16ae61f9e1a","tid":965734,"uid":200882,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"真係好撚痴線 話說之前好似有個後生女做市長 唔知佢死咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca8969c385aa51c6dcf80067944e9c796132832","tid":965734,"uid":55924,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"1年850個<br />\n每日3個咁濟<br />\n姐係班賊日日出動<br />\n好撚忙下😂"},{"pid":"5cd02956b4836910902ce1d61d19dbeab